<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Vidhi Vora — About</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@500;700;900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap');

  :root{
    --teal:#0F3B3D;
    --coral:#FF6B5B;
    --yellow:#FFC857;
    --cream:#FFF8F0;
    --ink:#16213A;
    --lavender:#B8A9E8;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  body{margin:0;background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;}
  .wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 80px;}

  /* ---------- TOP BAR / HERO ---------- */
  .hero{
    background:var(--teal);
    color:var(--cream);
    border-radius:0 0 32px 32px;
    padding:48px 24px 60px;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero::before{
    content:"✈";
    position:absolute;
    top:20px; right:40px;
    font-size:120px;
    opacity:0.06;
    transform:rotate(20deg);
  }
  .hero-inner{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:32px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .photo-slot{
    width:120px;height:150px;flex-shrink:0;
    border:3px dashed rgba(255,248,240,0.5);
    border-radius:10px;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;
    font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,248,240,0.6);
    padding:8px;
  }
  .hero-text .eyebrow{
    font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;
    font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--yellow);margin-bottom:8px;
  }
  .hero-text h1{
    font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:900;
    font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,52px);margin:0 0 8px;
  }
  .hero-text p{font-size:17px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,248,240,0.85);max-width:560px;margin:0;}
  .hero-tags{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:16px;}
  .hero-tags span{
    font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;
    border:1px solid rgba(255,248,240,0.4);
    padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;
  }

  /* ---------- SECTION LABEL ---------- */
  .section-label{
    font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:2px;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--coral);margin:64px 0 8px;
  }
  .section-title{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:30px;margin:0 0 32px;}

  /* ---------- FLIGHT PATH TIMELINE ---------- */
  .flightpath{position:relative;padding:40px 0 20px;}
  .route-line{
    position:absolute;top:60px;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,var(--ink) 0 8px,transparent 8px 16px);
    z-index:0;
  }
  .stops{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;position:relative;z-index:1;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:24px;}
  .stop{width:180px;text-align:center;}
  .stop .pin{
    width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--cream);border:2px solid var(--ink);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    margin:0 auto 10px;font-size:18px;position:relative;top:38px;
  }
  .stop.final .pin{background:var(--yellow);border-color:var(--coral);}
  .stop .code{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--coral);}
  .stop .role{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin:4px 0 2px;}
  .stop .yrs{font-size:12px;color:#6b6f80;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;}
  .stop .note{font-size:12px;margin-top:6px;color:#555;line-height:1.4;}

  /* ---------- STAMP GRID (fun facts / personality / boundaries) ---------- */
  .stamp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:24px;}
  .stamp{
    background:var(--cream);
    border:2px solid var(--ink);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:22px 20px;
    position:relative;
    transform:rotate(var(--r,-1.5deg));
  }
  .stamp:nth-child(2){--r:1deg;}
  .stamp:nth-child(3){--r:-2deg;}
  .stamp:nth-child(4){--r:1.5deg;}
  .stamp:nth-child(5){--r:-1deg;}
  .stamp:nth-child(6){--r:2deg;}
  .stamp::after{
    content:"APPROVED";
    position:absolute;top:12px;right:14px;
    font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;
    color:var(--coral);border:1px solid var(--coral);border-radius:4px;
    padding:2px 6px;transform:rotate(8deg);opacity:0.8;
  }
  .stamp .icon{font-size:26px;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;}
  .stamp h3{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:17px;margin:0 0 6px;}
  .stamp p{font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;color:#333;}

  /* ---------- QUOTE POSTCARD ---------- */
  .postcard{
    background:var(--coral);color:var(--cream);
    border-radius:20px;padding:44px 32px;
    text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    margin-top:64px;
  }
  .postcard::before{
    content:"";position:absolute;inset:10px;
    border:1.5px dashed rgba(255,248,240,0.5);border-radius:12px;
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .postcard .mark{font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:0.85;margin-bottom:14px;}
  .postcard blockquote{
    font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;font-style:italic;
    font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);margin:0;line-height:1.4;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;
  }
  .postcard .sig{margin-top:16px;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;opacity:0.85;}

  /* ---------- PHOTO GALLERY PLACEHOLDER ---------- */
  .gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(140px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:24px;}
  .gpic{
    aspect-ratio:3/4;border:3px dashed #c9c2b4;border-radius:10px;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:#a49d8f;text-align:center;padding:8px;
    background:#fbf6ec;
  }

  @media(max-width:640px){
    .stops{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;}
    .route-line{display:none;}
    .stop{width:100%;text-align:left;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;}
    .stop .pin{position:static;margin:0;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ================= TOP BAR / HERO ================= -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="photo-slot">📷<br>passport photo<br>coming soon</div>
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">Boarding pass · Seat 1A · Priority</div>
      <h1>Hi, I'm Vidhi Vora</h1>
      <p>Professional problem-solver, part-time (okay, full-time) daydreamer of departure boards. Currently based in one city, permanently planning the next one.</p>
      <div class="hero-tags">
        <span>🧭 Mission: touch every state in India, then the map</span>
        <span>☕ Genz-certified</span>
        <span>📈 A little progress every day</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">

  <!-- ================= FLIGHT PATH TIMELINE ================= -->
  <div class="section-label">Flight history</div>
  <div class="section-title">Where I've been (professionally)</div>
  <div class="flightpath">
    <div class="route-line"></div>
    <div class="stops">
      <div class="stop">
        <div class="pin">🛫</div>
        <div class="code">CO-1</div>
        <div class="role">Company One</div>
        <div class="yrs">20XX — 20XX</div>
        <div class="note">Where it all began</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop">
        <div class="pin">✈️</div>
        <div class="code">CO-2</div>
        <div class="role">Company Two</div>
        <div class="yrs">20XX — 20XX</div>
        <div class="note">Leveled up, learned a lot</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop">
        <div class="pin">📍</div>
        <div class="code">NOW</div>
        <div class="role">Current Role</div>
        <div class="yrs">20XX — present</div>
        <div class="note">You are here</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stop final">
        <div class="pin">🌍</div>
        <div class="code">TBD</div>
        <div class="role">The Whole Map</div>
        <div class="yrs">destination: everywhere</div>
        <div class="note">Final boarding call</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:12px;color:#888;font-family:'Space Mono',monospace;">* swap in your real company names, roles & years above</p>

  <!-- ================= FUN FACTS / PERSONALITY STAMPS ================= -->
  <div class="section-label">Customs declaration</div>
  <div class="section-title">Fun facts, personality & house rules</div>
  <div class="stamp-grid">
    <div class="stamp">
      <span class="icon">🗺️</span>
      <h3>Life goal: collect places, not things</h3>
      <p>The dream is to set foot in every Indian state — and honestly, every country too. Consider this your fair warning: I will be taking holidays.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stamp">
      <span class="icon">⏰</span>
      <h3>9-to-6 means 9-to-6</h3>
      <p>Fully focused during working hours. Overtime is welcome — with pay. Unpaid overtime is a concept I have chosen not to believe in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stamp">
      <span class="icon">📵</span>
      <h3>Once I clock out, I'm off the grid</h3>
      <p>No work calls or messages after hours, please. That time belongs to my people, my plans, and me.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stamp">
      <span class="icon">🌱</span>
      <h3>Give me a fair shot to learn</h3>
      <p>I ask questions because I actually want to get it right. Be patient, skip the scolding, and let the results speak once I've figured it out — they will.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stamp">
      <span class="icon">🎈</span>
      <h3>Family & friends come first</h3>
      <p>I work to fund the trips and to be there for the people I love — every function, every "we need you," every celebration. Those days are non-negotiable and don't need an explanation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stamp">
      <span class="icon">💛</span>
      <h3>Delicate corporate girl energy</h3>
      <p>Kind words get the best out of me. I take feedback seriously — I just don't do well with scolding, and honestly, who does?</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ================= QUOTE POSTCARD ================= -->
  <div class="postcard">
    <div class="mark">✈ wish you were here — postcard from my desk</div>
    <blockquote>"A little progress each day adds up to big results."</blockquote>
    <div class="sig">— the motto I actually live by, Vidhi</div>
  </div>

  <!-- ================= PHOTO GALLERY PLACEHOLDER ================= -->
  <div class="section-label">Photo album</div>
  <div class="section-title">Snapshots (loading soon)</div>
  <div class="gallery">
    <div class="gpic">add photo</div>
    <div class="gpic">add photo</div>
    <div class="gpic">add photo</div>
    <div class="gpic">add photo</div>
    <div class="gpic">add photo</div>
  </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
